                        "displayName": "Wes McKinney",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "America/New_York"
                    },
                    "body": "IMHO we should consider a slimmed down data structure for the implementation of {{ExecBatch}} that does not use {{arrow::util::variant}}, considering that we only ever will have either {{ArrayData}} or {{Scalar}} as value types. The overhead of slicing {{ArrayData}} objects is also non-trivial",
